Recommended build instructions:

To build changes: 
browserify -t [ babelify --presets [ react ] ] index.js -o ../server/static/index.js

If watch for changes and automagically build:
watchify  -t [ babelify --presets [ react ] ] index.js -o ../server/static/index.js



Installation instructions:

Requirements:
Node.js

browserify: -Bundles all JS files into one (See browserify.org)
  To install globally: npm install -g browserify
watchify: -Watches for file changes and automatically rebuilds changed files. Recommended, but not required.
  To install globally: npm -g watchify

Dependencies in package.json:
  To install: npm install


